FBIS3-23279 "jptot011__l94095" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 10 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Police Arrest Qiryat Arba' Man for Not handing Over Weapon TA1003162694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1600 GMT 10 Mar 94 TA1003162694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The Judaea District police have arrested Avraham Sheier, a resident of Qiryat Arba', who refused to obey an injunction ordering him to turn in his weapon. Our correspondent Gil Litman reports that the police today confiscated the weapon of another Qiryat Arba' resident.
